title: Rosetta Stone and Languages V3
description:
Rosetta Stone V3.

Contains The Following :

Power ISO - To Mount the discs.

Rosetta Stone v3 application
Rosetta Stone RS.3.0.57.UPDATE
Rosetta Stone V3 Patch

Arabic lvls 1 and 2
French lvl 1
Spanish (spain) lvs 1 - 3
Spanish (latin america) lvs 1 - 3
Italian lvls 1 -3
German lvls 1 -3



How It Works.

Mount the application.
Install.
Close.
Run Update.
Close.
Move Patch to Install Directory.
Run Patch.
Open Rosetta Stone.
Mount Language.
Install the langauge through Rosetta Stone.
To activate. enter all X for the code.
It will ask you to activate by phone. Do it.
Enter all 1 for the code.
You are good to go.
